This is the Perl module Dist::Joseki.

## Installation

Dist::Joseki installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up, you
should just be able to do

    % cpan Dist::Joseki

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Dist::Joseki documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Dist::Joseki

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

